description:
Josefina Bermudez Avila, Roxana Suarez, Fabian Peralta and, Sebastian Achaval dance “Rebeldía” by Miguel Caló, sung by Raúl Iriarte, at the 5th Łódź Tango Salon Festival 2015 in Łódź, Poland.
